{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p>Pour créer un ebook à partir d&#x27;un fichier markdown, il est possible d&#x27;utiliser Pandoc sur <a class=\"\" href=\"/linux\">Linux</a>.</p>\n<h2>Installation de Pandoc sur Linux</h2><p>Sur Ubuntu et Debian :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">apt update &amp;&amp; apt install -y pandoc texlive texlive-latex-extra\n</code></pre></div><p>Sur Arch Linux :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">pacman -S --noconfirm pandoc texlive-bin texlive-core\n</code></pre></div><h2>Création d&#x27;un ebook au format epub</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">pandoc input.md -o output.epub\n</code></pre></div><h2>Création d&#x27;un ebook au format pdf</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">pandoc input.md -o output.pdf\n</code></pre></div><h2>Création d&#x27;un ebook au format mobi</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">pandoc input.md -o output.mobi\n</code></pre></div><h2>Création d&#x27;un ebook avec Docker</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run -it -v $PWD:/mnt pandoc/core input.md -o /mnt/output.mobi\n</code></pre></div><h2>Ajouter une cover</h2><p>Pour ajouter une cover :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">pandoc input.md --epub-cover-image cover.png -o output.epub\n</code></pre></div></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Créer un ebook à partir d'un fichier markown.md","fileName":"Créer un ebook à partir d'un fichier markown","title":"Créer un ebook à partir d'un fichier markown","comments":true,"permalink":"creer-un-ebook-a-partir-d'un-fichier-markown","datePublished":"2021-06-27T19:19","dateUpdated":"2021-06-27T19:19","publish":true,"rss":true,"note":"67"},"__N_SSG":true}